channel.title: Swift Pkz V1 - 317 Client, NEW GUI, NEW SPRITES, IP CHANGER
channel.description:
Hey guys, releasing my new client now Swift Pkz V1
Change Log from V0.5 -
- New Sprites - New Gui - Fixed Bugs - Fixed Crashing - Added IP Changer - New Customs (Models created by me)
I made this on my old laptop which was windows vista and since upgraded to windows 7 as my windows vista had a power failure. I managed to backup my files along with the client i have been working on a fair time but have no use for it as windows 7 is very buggy with java so the client will not open up etc. Thought it would be nice releasing it since i have no use and someone else will. Enjoy
(NOTE: Could someone please take picture of the client and post it here since i cannot open java on windows 7, much appreciated :)
Download Link -
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?mf5m5xttufz]http://www.mediafire.com/?mf5m5xttufz[/url]
